    <headline>Frequent lightning, yellow level, Parts of Nordland and Trøndelag, 2022-06-30T15:20:00+00:00, 2022-06-30T21:00:00+00:00</headline>
    <description>Widespread/scattered thunderstorms have been observed with frequent lightning over the inner parts of Nordland. The thunderstorm is expected to continue until tonight. There are large local differences in intensity. Some places will not experience any thunderstorms. </description>
    <instruction>Stay up to date on the development of the weather and the weather forecast. Monitor the weather radar or lyn.met.no. Disconnect electrical appliances. Adjust driving speed according to the road/weather conditions. Seek shelter. Avoid open plains and large trees. Do not swim or bathe. </instruction>
